718464f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 71st Street (West)
718464f-a.text:
Central Park West, north from West 71st Street and showing apartment buildings facing Central Park. The Hotel Majestic is in the center, occupying the entire block front from 72nd to 73rd Streets. On the left are the Lorington and the Barnard respectively.
September 1914.
George L. Balgue.
